{"tid":1553054,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"9.9 埋大全日都要人！！！ (整合資訊)","createTime":"2019-09-08T13:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T04:55:16.000Z","uid":49938,"like":80,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"0cfa32aa0682946e7d808259923378bcdc6d5dec","tid":1553054,"uid":49938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:14:03.000Z","msg":"第一重炮係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鏈住理</span><br />\n集合時間係1800<br />\n首先希望大家由A1出口火車橋做起點，向poly library同尖東橋雙向出發，然後匯合返成一個大圈<br />\n然後視乎人數，會向黃埔方向延伸，希望去到poly舊hall果邊。另一邊都係視乎人數，睇下可唔可以由尖東橋一路延伸去尖沙咀海旁一帶。以上都係好視乎聽晚人數，如果唔夠人可能圈都圍唔成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以好靠大家幫手，多你一個好多<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全世界都黎得！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/connectpolyu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fconnectpolyu&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=f7a4e92d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/connectpolyu</a><br />\n呢個係人鏈tg link<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QnFACFR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQnFACFR.jpg&h=1c31ae77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二炮係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">理大開學禮</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為我地實在唔想大家罷完課留係屋企訓覺，甚或有同學話因為罷完冇野做先去上堂，所以我地搞左個開學禮，務求做到罷課不罷學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲請埋陳沛然醫生同鄺仔到時作分享，各位冇理由唔黎啦掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/09E2hFR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F09E2hFR.jpg&h=def9ef24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bipJMzb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbipJMzb.jpg&h=3dc18de8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三炮當日朝早仲有一班理大護理同學自發嘅罷課集會，時間係每日1130-1330，果d話attendance好重要罷唔到課嘅同學，你唔會一星期五日呢段時間都要上堂掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁你就去支持啦仲望<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rvXOXFS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrvXOXFS.jpg&h=e78be9a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後係幫學生會/罷委/奧雲叔/其他人宣傳，其實仲有好多形形色色嘅活動畀大家參與，例如星期二請左毛姨姨教英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mXGcEUd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmXGcEUd.png&h=d9b76f72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁遲出post因為想係港島區手足同聽日活動宣傳之間取平衡，請各位見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊post如下：<br />\n<br />\n［突發］埋大9.9 吹大雞鏈住理<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544102</a>"},{"pid":"a1c7f6d66536cb24cd9cfc092a2c6a3fd076ae52","tid":1553054,"uid":272292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:14:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca59c061c8cebb6eef0102f3dee7a055c8943b3a","tid":1553054,"uid":172164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:18:19.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"cd8a5e03c1663e84ed1df3e21c27d2b86190260b","tid":1553054,"uid":183950,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad574f2a8676042bf7a6a51e02b9f2e9207f2a5","tid":1553054,"uid":172164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:18:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ee331b9df18c6e6121d150d2165e1d23d7aa0b7","tid":1553054,"uid"